- I received a broadcast from trial5_robot1. It seems trial5_robot1 is trying to discover other robots. I will wait to see if other robots respond. I will give it 5 seconds.

```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 5000 }
]
```

I have reached the target position (125, 56.7) as instructed by trial5_robot2. I will now broadcast my position and wait for further instructions.

```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial5_robot3: I have reached (125, 56.7)." }
]
```

I will wait to give trial5_robot1 some time to respond. I will wait for 10 seconds.

```
[
  { "cmd": "timeout", "parm": 10000 }
]
```

I have sensed my position and distances to the boundary. Now I will broadcast my boundary information.

```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial5_robot3: My distances to the boundary are front: 143.5, right: 175.0, back: 56.8, left: 125.3. My position is (125.2, 56.7), and my orientation is 87.1." }
]
```

trial5_robot2 does not have the object. I also do not have the object. Since none of us have the object and we cannot sense the object, we cannot fulfill trial5_robot1's request. I should inform trial5_robot1 about this.

```
[
  { "cmd": "broadcast", "data": "This is trial5_robot3: trial5_robot1, neither trial5_robot2 nor I have the object. We cannot sense the object, so we cannot move it to the center." }
]
```

I have finish the execution and waited for a long time. There are no new instructions. I will enter idle mode.

```
[
  { "cmd": "idle" }
]
```
